OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,FThe Archbishop of Wales has admitted a
OL,7,Fculture of 'turning a blind eye' led
OL,8,Fto "horrendous" abuse at the hands of
OL,9,Fa former Bishop.
OL,11,FArchbishop Cherry Vann told ITV Cymru
OL,12,FWales of her shock at reading a
OL,13,F"sobering" independent review
OL,14,Fcommissioned by the Church, which
OL,15,Ffound that several members did not act
OL,16,Fafter an allegation of sexual assault
OL,17,Fwas made against the former Bishop of
OL,18,FSwansea and Brecon, Anthony Pierce, in
OL,19,F1993.
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@OO]uD@AOUuD@JO]
