OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,FSenior clerics in the Church in Wales
OL,7,Fknew Pierce was accused of sexually
OL,8,Fassaulting a child, but did not act
OL,9,Fand still allowed him to be promoted
OL,10,Fto Bishop of Brecon and Swansea,
OL,11,Faccording to a critical review
OL,12,Fpublished on Thursday (February 26).
OL,14,FThe review says the Church's handling
OL,15,Fof Pierce's case at the time was
OL,16,F"wholly inappropriate and inadequate".
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
