OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,FAmong those referenced in the review
OL,7,Fare several Archbishops of Wales,
OL,8,Fincluding John Davies and Rowan
OL,9,FWilliams, the former Archbishop of
OL,10,FCanterbury.
OL,12,FThose most seriously criticised in the
OL,13,F131-page document include Bishop Dewi
OL,14,FBridges, Archdeacon Brian James,
OL,15,FArchdeacon Wynford Rees and former
OL,16,FArchbishop of Wales Alwyn Rice Jones,
OL,17,Fall of whom have since died.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
