OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772193824
OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,F"It's a very sobering review,"
OL,7,FArchbishop Vann said. "I was shocked
OL,8,Fto read the report and I think anybody
OL,9,Fwho reads the report will be similarly
OL,10,Fshocked."
OL,12,FShe continued: "It's a shame on the
OL,13,FChurch that these things happened.
OL,14,FIt's horrendous to know that at the
OL,15,Fhands of an ordained person in the
OL,16,Fchurch, two people at least that we
OL,17,Fknow about have been so traumatised
OL,18,Fand abused."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@^O]oD@WOUrD@IO]tD@POUzD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/7
