OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,FThe allegations against Pierce only
OL,7,Fcame to light last year when he was
OL,8,Fjailed after admitting to sexually
OL,9,Fassaulting a child under the age of 16
OL,10,Fwhile working as a parish priest at
OL,11,FHoly Cross Church in Swansea.
OL,13,FThe Archbishop said the Church cannot
OL,14,Fbe sure if there are no more victims
OL,15,Fof abuse, but called on people to come
OL,16,Fforward if they had any concerns.
OL,18,FShe said: "There could well be people
OL,19,Fout there who have been abused, who
OL,20,Fhaven't chosen to report it or haven't
OL,21,Ffelt able to report their abuse."
OL,26,@zD@KOU}D@aO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
