PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772193824
OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,F"One of the things I want to do today,
OL,7,Fgoing forward, is to encourage anybody
OL,8,Fwho has been abused or who has
OL,9,Fconcerns within the Church in Wales
OL,10,Fabout safeguarding to come forward and
OL,11,Freport it so that we can deal with it
OL,12,Fappropriately."
OL,14,FOn Thursday (26 February) morning,
OL,15,FSouth Wales Police confirmed the
OL,16,Finvestigation into Pierce remains live.
OL,18,FAsked if she thought the Church was in
OL,19,Fcrisis, the Archbishop admitted,
OL,20,F"There are crises that we are having
OL,21,Fto deal with.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@OO]|D@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
