OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1772193824
OL,3,CArchbishop of Wales reacts to
OL,4,C'horrendous' child sexual abuse report
OL,6,F"There's an awful lot about the Church
OL,7,Fin Wales that is good. But there are
OL,8,Fthings of a serious nature that we are
OL,9,Fhaving to deal with, and we are
OL,10,Fdealing with."
OL,12,FAlthough she added, "I am confident
OL,13,Fthat we now have processes in place
OL,14,Fthat will address things like this
OL,15,Fgoing forward. The report, as you
OL,16,Fprobably know, makes a lot of
OL,17,Frecommendations. A lot of those are
OL,18,Falready in place, I've already been
OL,19,Fimplemented."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]tD@UOU{D@MO]
